        "evidence": "<p>Ask if the patient has more than 12 years of education, not including kindergarten years.</p>",
        "facts": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Interpretation:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">MoCA Score &lt;26 points is 90% sensitive for mild cognitive impairment and 100% sensitive for Alzheimer&rsquo;s disease.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Although the average MoCA score for Alzheimer&nbsp;patients is much lower than for MCI patients, there exists some overlap, such that the cutoff score is the same for both; the presence of functional impairment should distinguish them, not their MoCA Score.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
        "estimation": [],
        "primary_complains": [
            "Neurologic Deficit"
        ],
        "disease_treated": [
            "Dementia"
        ],
        "logic": "var calc_output =[];\nvar one = parseFloat(one);\nvar two  = parseFloat(two);\nvar three = parseFloat(three);\nvar four = parseFloat(four);\nvar five = parseFloat(five);\nvar six = parseFloat(six);\nvar seven = parseFloat(seven);\nvar eight = parseFloat(eight);\nvar nine = parseFloat(nine);\nvar ten  = parseFloat(ten);\nvar eleven = parseFloat(eleven);\nvar twelve = parseFloat(twelve);\nvar thirteen = parseFloat(thirteen);\nvar fourteen = parseFloat(fourteen);\nvar fifteen = parseFloat(fifteen);\nvar sixteen = parseFloat(sixteen);\nvar seventeen = parseFloat(seventeen);\nvar eighteen = parseFloat(eighteen);\nvar age = parseFloat(age);\n\n\nvar score = one +\ntwo  +\nthree +\nfour +\nfive +\nsix +\neight +\nnine +\nten  +\neleven +\ntwelve +\nthirteen +\nfourteen +\nfifteen +\nsixteen +\nseventeen +\neighteen + age;\n\nvar risk = \"Lower scores indicate more cognitive impairment; cutoff of <26 points is 90% sensitive for mild cognitive impairment and 100% sensitive for Alzheimer's disease\"\n\n//results\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: risk\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Score',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: risk   \n});\n\n",
